  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231920/extras/0cb22b8d4d7f60763500aab9957ae4e9.avif?t=1756969901\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231920/extras_big/0cb22b8d4d7f60763500aab9957ae4e9.avif?t=1756969901 width=800 height=458 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Special thanks to Haetae for granting permission to use the character and artwork.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It requires at least 5G of VRAM to run properly.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Requires at least a Ryzen 2600 CPU and a graphics card equivalent to or higher than an RTX 2060 with DirectX 12 support.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Introduction</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Developer</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mainly developed by one person, with 1–2 others contributing on a case-by-case basis.</p></li></ul></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Genre</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Action RPG (Soulslike Style)</p></li></ul></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Development Status</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Early Access / Demo</p></li></ul></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Core Systems</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Divine Orb Growth, Challenging Combat, Multiverse Exploration through Portals</p></li></ul></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Features</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Variable Combat Styles(Planned), Powerful Boss Battles</p></li></ul></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>World & Gameplay</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A peaceful morning somewhere in Yeongwol Mountain.<br>However, the once-familiar mountain trail is strangely twisted, and a mysterious portal reveals an entirely different world.<br>Though you manage to return home, time around your house flows abnormally fast.<br>The path leading down to the city has completely vanished, and people caught in the phenomenon begin taking shelter in your house.<br>Among them are those who may not even belong to this world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You must uncover the reason behind this distorted world—and restore it.Players will travel across multiple connected worlds and explore diverse regions.<br>Along the way, they will encounter various enemies and occasionally defeat powerful foes for special rewards.<br>The Divine Orb system allows players to adapt their combat styles and face stronger enemies.<br>Players will discover hidden clues in each region and interact with NPCs to piece together the overarching story. <i>(Story-related clues will be expanded through future updates.)</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Main Regions</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Yeongwol Mountain & Rift in Space-Time</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The beginning where reality and unreality intersect. Portals connect to other worlds.</p></li></ul></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231920/extras/5afa357955df4194e52e07cc6024682a.avif?t=1756969901\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231920/extras_big/5afa357955df4194e52e07cc6024682a.avif?t=1756969901 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >▲ Basement</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231920/extras/7da38116b5b40a8ed61895a918edc48d.avif?t=1756969901\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231920/extras_big/7da38116b5b40a8ed61895a918edc48d.avif?t=1756969901 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >▲ Portal to Another World</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Twisted Forest</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A forest once home to nature spirits, now entangled with invading goblins.</p></li></ul></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231920/extras/aed4af6c3abef5493e531fba4d191d3c.avif?t=1756969901\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231920/extras_big/aed4af6c3abef5493e531fba4d191d3c.avif?t=1756969901 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231920/extras/843b245b563c6bd62457035ab028d99d.avif?t=1756969901\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231920/extras_big/843b245b563c6bd62457035ab028d99d.avif?t=1756969901 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Desert Canyon</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A space where past and present collide.  <i>(Currently under development)</i></p></li></ul></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231920/extras/7ce21a3f61adb4107b4d355db22dc2e1.avif?t=1756969901\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231920/extras_big/7ce21a3f61adb4107b4d355db22dc2e1.avif?t=1756969901 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231920/extras/72e33e3a6b33ed96ffc8092a0e01471f.avif?t=1756969901\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231920/extras_big/72e33e3a6b33ed96ffc8092a0e01471f.avif?t=1756969901 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Snowfield</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Planned</p></li></ul></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Joseon-era World</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Planned</p></li></ul></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >???</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Planned</p></li></ul></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Core Systems</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Divine Orb & Fragments</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As the world changes, your power shatters and scatters.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You must collect fragments to enhance and expand your abilities.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>A core growth system that allows flexible changes in combat style.</i></p></li></ul></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Divine Fragments</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Equip fragments into the Orb’s \"Core\" to apply new traits.</p></li></ul></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Divine Core System</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock internal slots in each core to gain further enhancements.</p></li></ul></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Traits</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each fragment grants special properties and modifies combat behavior.</p></li></ul></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The combination of Divine Fragments and Cores can fundamentally change your combat style.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231920/extras/e36dd47b8122417c14dd4e1626d1be57.avif?t=1756969901\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231920/extras_big/e36dd47b8122417c14dd4e1626d1be57.avif?t=1756969901 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >▲ Divine Orb Editing UI</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Growth</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Soulslike Growth System</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Defeat enemies or use items to collect Souls and level up.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose one of the following stats to improve: HP / Mana / Stamina / Strength / Dexterity / Intelligence / Willpower</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231920/extras/4e5ff800d9c5bb9263270c7b06efadd9.avif?t=1756969901\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231920/extras_big/4e5ff800d9c5bb9263270c7b06efadd9.avif?t=1756969901 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >▲ Level-Up UI</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Growth through the Divine Orb</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlocking Core slots grants new powers and strengthens existing ones.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fragments are acquired through exploration. Slots can be unlocked, and attributes can be added to fragments. Fully unlocking a line of slots grants special bonuses. Each Core has a different slot structure and line arrangement.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231920/extras/a6b7eba28e34d1495d711ae603836399.avif?t=1756969901\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231920/extras_big/a6b7eba28e34d1495d711ae603836399.avif?t=1756969901 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >▲ Slot Unlocking UI</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231920/extras/ce996b62c1f71ba2f567b843d45b899a.avif?t=1756969901\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231920/extras_big/ce996b62c1f71ba2f567b843d45b899a.avif?t=1756969901 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >▲ Fragment Enhancement UI</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Growth via Equipment System</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Equip weapons (Sprites), armor (Auras), and accessories (Ring).</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sprites and Auras can be strengthened and enhanced with attributes.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231920/extras/c8cc6aeafc4ee14ca77b16ef3fa005e8.avif?t=1756969901\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231920/extras_big/c8cc6aeafc4ee14ca77b16ef3fa005e8.avif?t=1756969901 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >▲ Equipment Enhancement UI</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231920/extras/fbef0c242f572c8a699cf2d7891557fc.avif?t=1756969901\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231920/extras_big/fbef0c242f572c8a699cf2d7891557fc.avif?t=1756969901 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >▲ Elemental Infusion UI</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Combat Styles & Characters</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Default Playable Character</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >White Tiger (Playable)</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Melee combat focused on dodging and striking</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Intuitive controls, close-range combat</p></li></ul></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Wolf (Planned)</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Stack-based mid-range combat using talismans</p></li></ul></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fox (Planned)</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >High-risk, high-reward counter-attack focused combat</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Has no HP; dies upon exceeding a certain number of hits</p></li></ul></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each Sprites (weapon) uses different animation sets, enabling a wide variety of play styles beyond the base characters.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>NPC</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enhancement & Elemental Infusion (See: Equipment System)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Stat boosts and slot unlocking for Divine Orb (See: Orb Growth System)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Special item exchange via boss soul shards</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231920/extras/d5ebbaff147a8d1dd4f7cde7e0a98a3b.avif?t=1756969901\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231920/extras_big/d5ebbaff147a8d1dd4f7cde7e0a98a3b.avif?t=1756969901 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >▲ Boss Reward Exchange UI</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Returning Lost Parcels : Find and return lost NPC parcels during exploration to unlock new shop items.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231920/extras/3ad5a9cf9f446ea8cec060d1762cb259.avif?t=1756969901\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231920/extras_big/3ad5a9cf9f446ea8cec060d1762cb259.avif?t=1756969901 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >▲ NPC Dialogue After Returning Lost Bundle</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Potion Enhancement : Bring specific materials to NPCs to increase potion charges and healing power.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231920/extras/dd370b1d8e830c574f90d1d78523263e.avif?t=1756969901\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231920/extras_big/dd370b1d8e830c574f90d1d78523263e.avif?t=1756969901 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >▲ Potion Upgrade UI</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Some NPCs or characters may not have 3D models.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Support</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >ko-fi : </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Email: <a href=\"mailto:bu30808dev@gmail.com\">bu30808dev@gmail.com</a></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discord(KR): </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231920/extras/0cb22b8d4d7f60763500aab9957ae4e9.avif?t=1756969901\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231920/extras_big/0cb22b8d4d7f60763500aab9957ae4e9.avif?t=1756969901 width=800 height=458 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Special thanks to Haetae for granting permission to use the character and artwork.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It requires at least 5G of VRAM to run properly.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Requires at least a Ryzen 2600 CPU and a graphics card equivalent to or higher than an RTX 2060 with DirectX 12 support.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Introduction</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Developer</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mainly developed by one person, with 1–2 others contributing on a case-by-case basis.</p></li></ul></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Genre</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Action RPG (Soulslike Style)</p></li></ul></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Development Status</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Early Access / Demo</p></li></ul></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Core Systems</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Divine Orb Growth, Challenging Combat, Multiverse Exploration through Portals</p></li></ul></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Features</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Variable Combat Styles(Planned), Powerful Boss Battles</p></li></ul></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>World & Gameplay</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A peaceful morning somewhere in Yeongwol Mountain.<br>However, the once-familiar mountain trail is strangely twisted, and a mysterious portal reveals an entirely different world.<br>Though you manage to return home, time around your house flows abnormally fast.<br>The path leading down to the city has completely vanished, and people caught in the phenomenon begin taking shelter in your house.<br>Among them are those who may not even belong to this world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You must uncover the reason behind this distorted world—and restore it.Players will travel across multiple connected worlds and explore diverse regions.<br>Along the way, they will encounter various enemies and occasionally defeat powerful foes for special rewards.<br>The Divine Orb system allows players to adapt their combat styles and face stronger enemies.<br>Players will discover hidden clues in each region and interact with NPCs to piece together the overarching story. <i>(Story-related clues will be expanded through future updates.)</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Main Regions</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Yeongwol Mountain & Rift in Space-Time</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The beginning where reality and unreality intersect. Portals connect to other worlds.</p></li></ul></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231920/extras/5afa357955df4194e52e07cc6024682a.avif?t=1756969901\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231920/extras_big/5afa357955df4194e52e07cc6024682a.avif?t=1756969901 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >▲ Basement</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231920/extras/7da38116b5b40a8ed61895a918edc48d.avif?t=1756969901\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231920/extras_big/7da38116b5b40a8ed61895a918edc48d.avif?t=1756969901 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >▲ Portal to Another World</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Twisted Forest</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A forest once home to nature spirits, now entangled with invading goblins.</p></li></ul></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231920/extras/aed4af6c3abef5493e531fba4d191d3c.avif?t=1756969901\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231920/extras_big/aed4af6c3abef5493e531fba4d191d3c.avif?t=1756969901 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231920/extras/843b245b563c6bd62457035ab028d99d.avif?t=1756969901\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231920/extras_big/843b245b563c6bd62457035ab028d99d.avif?t=1756969901 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Desert Canyon</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A space where past and present collide.  <i>(Currently under development)</i></p></li></ul></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231920/extras/7ce21a3f61adb4107b4d355db22dc2e1.avif?t=1756969901\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231920/extras_big/7ce21a3f61adb4107b4d355db22dc2e1.avif?t=1756969901 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231920/extras/72e33e3a6b33ed96ffc8092a0e01471f.avif?t=1756969901\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231920/extras_big/72e33e3a6b33ed96ffc8092a0e01471f.avif?t=1756969901 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Snowfield</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Planned</p></li></ul></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Joseon-era World</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Planned</p></li></ul></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >???</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Planned</p></li></ul></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Core Systems</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Divine Orb & Fragments</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As the world changes, your power shatters and scatters.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You must collect fragments to enhance and expand your abilities.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>A core growth system that allows flexible changes in combat style.</i></p></li></ul></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Divine Fragments</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Equip fragments into the Orb’s \"Core\" to apply new traits.</p></li></ul></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Divine Core System</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock internal slots in each core to gain further enhancements.</p></li></ul></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Traits</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each fragment grants special properties and modifies combat behavior.</p></li></ul></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The combination of Divine Fragments and Cores can fundamentally change your combat style.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231920/extras/e36dd47b8122417c14dd4e1626d1be57.avif?t=1756969901\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231920/extras_big/e36dd47b8122417c14dd4e1626d1be57.avif?t=1756969901 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >▲ Divine Orb Editing UI</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Growth</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Soulslike Growth System</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Defeat enemies or use items to collect Souls and level up.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose one of the following stats to improve: HP / Mana / Stamina / Strength / Dexterity / Intelligence / Willpower</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231920/extras/4e5ff800d9c5bb9263270c7b06efadd9.avif?t=1756969901\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231920/extras_big/4e5ff800d9c5bb9263270c7b06efadd9.avif?t=1756969901 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >▲ Level-Up UI</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Growth through the Divine Orb</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlocking Core slots grants new powers and strengthens existing ones.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fragments are acquired through exploration. Slots can be unlocked, and attributes can be added to fragments. Fully unlocking a line of slots grants special bonuses. Each Core has a different slot structure and line arrangement.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231920/extras/a6b7eba28e34d1495d711ae603836399.avif?t=1756969901\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231920/extras_big/a6b7eba28e34d1495d711ae603836399.avif?t=1756969901 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >▲ Slot Unlocking UI</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231920/extras/ce996b62c1f71ba2f567b843d45b899a.avif?t=1756969901\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231920/extras_big/ce996b62c1f71ba2f567b843d45b899a.avif?t=1756969901 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >▲ Fragment Enhancement UI</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Growth via Equipment System</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Equip weapons (Sprites), armor (Auras), and accessories (Ring).</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sprites and Auras can be strengthened and enhanced with attributes.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231920/extras/c8cc6aeafc4ee14ca77b16ef3fa005e8.avif?t=1756969901\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231920/extras_big/c8cc6aeafc4ee14ca77b16ef3fa005e8.avif?t=1756969901 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >▲ Equipment Enhancement UI</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231920/extras/fbef0c242f572c8a699cf2d7891557fc.avif?t=1756969901\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231920/extras_big/fbef0c242f572c8a699cf2d7891557fc.avif?t=1756969901 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >▲ Elemental Infusion UI</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Combat Styles & Characters</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Default Playable Character</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >White Tiger (Playable)</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Melee combat focused on dodging and striking</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Intuitive controls, close-range combat</p></li></ul></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Wolf (Planned)</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Stack-based mid-range combat using talismans</p></li></ul></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fox (Planned)</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >High-risk, high-reward counter-attack focused combat</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Has no HP; dies upon exceeding a certain number of hits</p></li></ul></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each Sprites (weapon) uses different animation sets, enabling a wide variety of play styles beyond the base characters.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>NPC</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enhancement & Elemental Infusion (See: Equipment System)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Stat boosts and slot unlocking for Divine Orb (See: Orb Growth System)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Special item exchange via boss soul shards</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231920/extras/d5ebbaff147a8d1dd4f7cde7e0a98a3b.avif?t=1756969901\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231920/extras_big/d5ebbaff147a8d1dd4f7cde7e0a98a3b.avif?t=1756969901 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >▲ Boss Reward Exchange UI</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Returning Lost Parcels : Find and return lost NPC parcels during exploration to unlock new shop items.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231920/extras/3ad5a9cf9f446ea8cec060d1762cb259.avif?t=1756969901\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231920/extras_big/3ad5a9cf9f446ea8cec060d1762cb259.avif?t=1756969901 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >▲ NPC Dialogue After Returning Lost Bundle</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Potion Enhancement : Bring specific materials to NPCs to increase potion charges and healing power.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231920/extras/dd370b1d8e830c574f90d1d78523263e.avif?t=1756969901\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231920/extras_big/dd370b1d8e830c574f90d1d78523263e.avif?t=1756969901 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >▲ Potion Upgrade UI</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Some NPCs or characters may not have 3D models.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Support</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >ko-fi : </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Email: <a href=\"mailto:bu30808dev@gmail.com\">bu30808dev@gmail.com</a></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discord(KR): </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul>",
